Instalar Postman con Flatpak (recomendada si usas Mint 20+)
-------------------------------------------------------------

flatpak --version

sudo apt install flatpak

flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo

flatpak install flathub com.getpostman.Postman

flatpak run com.getpostman.Postman


Opción 3: Instalar manualmente desde el sitio oficial
------------------------------------------------------
wget https://dl.pstmn.io/download/latest/linux64 -O postman.tar.gz

sudo tar -xzf postman.tar.gz -C /opt

sudo ln -s /opt/Postman/Postman /usr/bin/postman

(Opcional) Crea un lanzador para el menú:
cat <<EOF | sudo tee /usr/share/applications/postman.desktop
[Desktop Entry]
Name=Postman
Exec=postman
Icon=/opt/Postman/app/resources/app/assets/icon.png
Type=Application
Categories=Development;
EOF


